/-- `Solution'` is a tuple given by a solution to `a ^ 3 + b ^ 3 = u * c ^ 3`,
where `a`, `b`, `c` and `u` are as in `FermatLastTheoremForThreeGen`.
See `Solution` for the actual structure on which we will do the descent. -/
