  (_root_.multiplicity (hŒ∂.toInteger - 1) S'.c).get (multiplicity_lambda_c_finite S')

/-- Given `S : Solution`, `S.multiplicity` is the multiplicity of `Œª` in `S.c`, as a natural
number. -/
